Package inventroyManager

package inventroyManager
  • Class
    Description
    App
    This Java Inventory Management System project uses CRUD to perform several inventory management operations.
    BookItem
    BookItem class extends Items class, implements Item Interface and represents book items
    CLIInterface
    This class organized operations on more visual and readable interface for the entire application
    ElectronicItem
    ElectrnonicItem class extends Items class, implements Item Interface and represents electronics items
    GroceryItem
    GroceryItem class extends Items class, implements Item Interface and represents grocery items
    InventoryManager
    This class controls inventory operations, manages inventory of BookItem,GroceryItem and ElectronicItem items and provides CRUD - Create New, Read, Update and Delete - operations.
    Item
    This class Provides interface for Items class
    Items
    Items class implements Item Interface, represents concrete and base class for GroceryItem, BookItem and ElectronicItem classes
